data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: Three adult men are standing in a field full of hay. The one on the left-hand side has short, curly hair and wears a blue vest and a pair of blue trousers. He is grabbing a bunch of hay with his left arm, leaning slightly towards his right side and looking down to the ground. The man behind him wears a white T-shirt and is bowing down to reach the hay on the ground. The guy on the right-hand side has relatively long, blonde hair, and wears a dark blue jacket and a pair of brown trousers. He is looking at the bunch of hay and using both of his hands to touch the hay. (115字)
